{"tid":2066522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「吉利汽車」激活員工，向國家釋放人材。","createTime":"2020-06-16T10:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T23:25:57.000Z","uid":202464,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9ce4828d90cfb34cf033b71bcb5196fb16c45e","tid":2066522,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:39:22.000Z","msg":"報道指出，吉利要提升團隊戰鬥力，適用於轉型的管理層和待激活員工，會就一線、非一線、管理層3類員工群組設計不同的培訓方案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n員工在培訓期間獲發放基本及職位工資，不發放績效工資。意味工資會大降，不少員工因而選擇離職。<br />\n<br />\n培訓完成後，有一定比例的員工不能過關，被解除勞動合約，且沒有賠償。<br />\n<br />\n報道又另引述消息稱，吉利藉計劃變相裁減20%普通員工及30%管理層。"},{"pid":"408c1e9890a8b4fa3528ada90c14c17f05c29b59","tid":2066522,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"發大財！全面小康。"},{"pid":"382529a7de1f9ebf6a0cfb68f41cf2992d5c274c","tid":2066522,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"地攤人才"},{"pid":"f5fe20e148851398ae1463909dba7d76bf7d3ebb","tid":2066522,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"382529a7de1f9ebf6a0cfb68f41cf2992d5c274c","tid":2066522,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"地攤人才"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"車房人才"},{"pid":"4914ded2d99e3424ea39aee4f4c270f612c76ca3","tid":2066522,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5fe20e148851398ae1463909dba7d76bf7d3ebb","tid":2066522,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"382529a7de1f9ebf6a0cfb68f41cf2992d5c274c","tid":2066522,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"地攤人才"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"車房人才"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:43:35.000Z","msg":"回鄉創業"},{"pid":"c90504dbc5ef61465293b4992fa823b32009cc5e","tid":2066522,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:51:36.000Z